headline: CoStar Group Named Among CRE’s Best Places to Work by GlobeSt.
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., September 23, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics, and 3D digital twin technology, announced today it has been named one of GlobeSt.’s Best Places to Work in CRE for 2025. The award recognizes organizations that set the standard in workplace culture, employee engagement, professional development, and long-term career satisfaction.
